        <p>The efreet (singular <a href="ch66s02.html#MonstersG17">efreeti</a>) are <a href="ch66s02.html#MonstersG8">genies</a> from the <a href="ch65s02.html#MonstersE-F7">Elemental</a> Plane of Fire.<a href="img/MonstersG.Efreeti.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersG.Efreeti.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
        <p>An <a href="ch66s02.html#MonstersG17">efreeti</a> stands about 12 feet tall and weighs about 2,000 pounds.</p>
        <p>Efreet speak Auran, Common, Ignan, and <a href="ch75.html#EpicMonsters(A-E)57">Infernal</a>.</p>
        <div class="sect4" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage">
            <div>
              <div>
