                <p><a href="ch22s03.html#CombatII52">Special Attacks</a> (see above): <span class="emphasis"><em>Change size</em></span>, <span class="emphasis"><em/></span> <a href="ch21s05.html#CombatI64">spell-like abilities.</a></p>
