              </li>
              <li style="list-style-type: disc">
                <p>Automatic Languages: Common. Bonus Languages: Abyssal, Aquan, Auran, Celestial, Ignan, <a href="ch75.html#EpicMonsters(A-E)57">Infernal</a>, Terran.</p>
